entries.femaleVariant: Look, I'm telling you this 'cause I like you and we got history – don't waste your time in school. Find something more your level.
Hahaha! You and your jokes. Choom, I finish this course, we'll be desk buddies at Militech.
We won't. They'll never take you. You're not me. Besides, who are your parents again?
Dad works down at the docks, mom's a waitress – but it doesn't matter. Not if I pass the exam.
Oh, it does. Your family and mine couldn't be more different. Can tell from the way you speak, from the way you... Pffft, sorry, but you look like you're ready for trick-or-treat.
Anyway, telling you for your own good. As a choom. The sooner you know your place, the better.
